意味もなく過ごしてた
I had been spending my days meaninglessly,

632
00:58:15,053 --> 00:58:20,553
日々を変えてくれたから
but you changed them for me.

633
00:58:20,553 --> 00:58:26,453
キミも泣くことぐらいあるよねってそっと
I want to gently stay by your side,

634
00:58:26,453 --> 00:58:31,553
寄り添ってあげたいな
thinking that you must have times when you cry too.

635
00:58:31,553 --> 00:58:36,953
終わらないでと願う 大切なMoment
This precious moment I pray won't end.

636
00:58:36,953 --> 00:58:42,453
知りたいでも知りたくはないの
I want to know, but I don't want to know,

637
00:58:42,453 --> 00:58:47,853
ここに閉じ込めて
lock it all up in here.

638
00:58:47,853 --> 00:58:55,953
ああ
Ah...

639
00:58:55,953 --> 00:59:00,953
たったひとつだけのわがまま
Please grant me just this one selfish wish:

640
00:59:00,953 --> 00:59:06,953
叶えてくれるかな 一番にしてよね
Make me your number one.

641
00:59:06,953 --> 00:59:12,453
運命と呼ぶにはまだまだ
It's still not enough

642
00:59:12,453 --> 00:59:17,453
足りない でもずっと
to call it destiny, but always,

643
00:59:17,453 --> 00:59:22,453
キミだけを
I'll be looking

644
00:59:22,453 --> 00:59:27,953
見てるよ
at only you.

645
00:59:46,953 --> 00:59:51,953
雪が煌めくこの花束
This bouquet where snow sparkles,

646
00:59:51,953 --> 00:59:57,453
抱えて祈ってる キミに渡せるように
I hold it and pray, so that I can give it to you.

647
00:59:57,453 --> 01:00:00,152
指先が震えるまでかな
Until my fingertips tremble...

648
01:00:00,165 --> 01:00:02,765
ちょっと まだまだ
Wait, there's still more

649
01:00:02,965 --> 01:00:04,665
待ってるね
I'll be waiting

650
01:00:05,265 --> 01:00:07,665
いつだって
Always

651
01:00:08,165 --> 01:00:10,665
この想い
These feelings

652
01:00:13,965 --> 01:00:18,665
届けよう
Let's send them out

653
01:00:24,665 --> 01:00:30,165
好きだよ
I love you

654
01:00:53,165 --> 01:01:21,165
2nd Anniversary! ♡

655
01:00:53,165 --> 01:01:21,165
雪民さんがいたから、今日のラミィがいて、明日のラミィもいるよ♡
Because the Yukimin were there, today's Lamy exists, and tomorrow's Lamy will too♡

656
01:00:53,165 --> 01:01:21,165
3年目も、みんなと一緒に色んな景色を見ていきたい！！
In the third year too, I want to see many different sights together with everyone!!

657
01:00:53,165 --> 01:01:21,165
いつも本当にありがとう！
Thank you so much as always!

658
